Package com.example.trialio.activities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExperimentActivity
    This activity opens an experiment when clicked from the main activity, and displays information about it
    ExperimentCreateActivity
    This activity allows a user to create an experiment, with full settings for the user to make it
    ExperimentSettingsActivity
    This activity allows an experiment owner to modify the settings of an experiment they own
    MainActivity  
    QRCodeActivity  
    StatActivity
    This activity allows a user to view stats about an experiment
    TrialActivity
    This activity shows a list of trials for an experiment when a user clicks the "trials" button from the experiment activity
    ViewUserActivity
    This activity allows a user to view their own profile and edit it to make changes to their username and contract info
